<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="run-after">run after</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>追赶；追求：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you run after two hares, you will catch neither. 
面面俱到，诸事未了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is said that John’s always running after younger women. 
据说约翰总是追求年轻女子。</p></div></div>